\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55da8e607c2fcf7e6cf044cff0e5702edab2e25b","tid":218870,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>狗仲會攻擊人添</blockquote><br />\n細狗多數吠姐 養寵物係一生一世諾言黎架<br />\n不過希望有人可以幫下我啦<br />\n借貸都借唔到<br />\n家庭主婦又要屋契又要電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工作證明又無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好下下都講錢啦<br />\n咁樣啲人會反感好難落搭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接啲仲好啦 呃呃哄哄做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係比仔哄得多先落搭 無哂啲錢"},{"pid":"b7f8e391b9c8dd30591015b9052d4830c6e04f80","tid":218870,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無錢重養狗？</blockquote><br />\n你生個仔出黎 單親 你無錢係未由佢死/孤兒院?"},{"pid":"55e44001d6fae8ab65911e423e7467bab16d7817","tid":218870,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠自己啦 人地幫你 幫得一時 幫唔到一世</blockquote><br />\n急要嘛....我都唔想<br />\n又無財務員工幫我借<br />\n連登話自己做財仔果幾位巴<br />\n公司名又唔講 仲要我出錢申請家居電話 仲要比哂全部個人資料佢"},{"pid":"1205f2f6e2a55bd3e0bf9c3870909ea1be95937d","tid":218870,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:16:34.000Z","msg":"搵件有錢佬俾人包 前題你要有返咁上下姿色"},{"pid":"60829dd39d63ce46f46b041d00a7b877dcd8e689","tid":218870,"uid":34436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T20:30:15.000Z","msg":"攞住綜援先啦 有咩事生活穩定d先算"},{"pid":"52677e0bda45e1eb0739afb28b05b662579704dc","tid":218870,"uid":63055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T23:46:48.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea07ec3a0d0522026813a6ed7fa718f1f50806d6","tid":218870,"uid":72212,"like":0,